_comment: This is a WordPress eXtended RSS file generated by WordPress as an export of your site.
It contains information about your site's posts, pages, comments, categories, and other content.
You may use this file to transfer that content from one site to another.
This file is not intended to serve as a complete backup of your site.
To import this information into a WordPress site follow these steps:
1. Log in to that site as an administrator.
2. Go to Tools: Import in the WordPress admin panel.
3. Install the "WordPress" importer from the list.
5. Upload this file using the form provided on that page.
6. You will first be asked to map the authors in this export file to users
on the site. For each author, you may choose to map to an
existing user on the site or to create a new user.
7. WordPress will then import each of the posts, pages, comments, categories, etc.
contained in this file into your site.

At Raw Furniture we make premium furniture from recycled timber. Our products are striking, sustainable, and totally unique. We specialise in farmhouse tables, bespoke cupboards, and antique-style furniture. We utilise rugged construction techniques that you won't find in factory-made furniture, which means our furniture is built to last. We are committed to recycling and upcycling used timber, giving each piece we make its own story. Check out the furniture page to see how we can transform your space with a piece made from character-filled recycled timber, or find out more about us, or about how our furniture is made. Raw Furniture is based in Adelaide, South Australia, but we routinely work with interstate customers. Please get in touch if you have any questions. Follow us on Facebookto receive updates of our latest furniture.

wp:meta_value._cdata: Raw Furniture - farmhouse tables, recycled timber furniture - Adelaide
Raw Furniture make premium furniture from recycled timber. Farmhouse tables and other rustic furniture, custom made. Based in Adelaide, SA.

content:encoded._cdata: Raw Furniture is Tony Dean and Pola Lekstan. Tony and Pola have over 30 years experience working with furniture. Starting with an antique and retro shop in the early 1980's Tony developed a passion for early Australian antique furniture. Pola's love was everything quirky and kitsch. After moving on to paint removal and restoration, Tony now makes beautiful farmhouse tables, sideboards, cupboards, and other industrial and antique-style furniture. Pola does everything from administering the business to assisting in the workshop. Together, they can help you find the perfect piece of furniture, or take you through the process of creating something custom-built to your specifications. Get in touch with Tony and Polatoday and find out more about what they can do for you.

Please get in touch with Raw Furniture if you have any questions, if you would like to arrange to see any of our current pieces of furniture, or to discuss a bespoke piece of furniture.

Phone

0421 524 137

Workshop

2 Leane Avenue, Allenby Gardens, SA, 5009, Australia [vsgmap address="2 Leane Avenue, 5009, Australia" height=200 info_window="A"]

Email

enquiries @ rawfurniture.com.au

Raw products are visually stunning, and built to the highest standards. Here are just a few reasons why you should choose us.

Handmade

All of our products are handmade in our Adelaide workshop. Every component has been hand-fitted and every joint inspected for quality.

Top quality and durable

We make all our products on-site, to our exacting standards. We construct our tables using mortice-and-tennon joints. This technique leads to superior strength and durability. Most factory-made tables have a rated lifespan of 5-10 years. We make tables that will last a lifetime.

Recycled and Sustainable

We make as much of every piece as possible from recycled timber, including all our table tops. Not only does this mean our furniture is sustainable, it also gives every piece we make it's own backstory!

Bespoke

If you like our style, but haven't seen the perfect piece of furniture on our products page, don't worry, we make to order. If you've got an unusual space to fit within, want something small that makes a statement, or want to go large, Raw can custom-build a piece to your specific requirements. We can adapt our construction methods to suit your purpose and budget. We will continue to work closely with you during the construction process.

Original and unique

Because every table we make is made from recycled or upcycled timber, you're guaranteed that the piece you put in your space will be one-of-a-kind. Raw Furniture will make sure that the individual character of the timber you choose will be on show.
